on on current working dir.\r\n``` json\r\n{\r\n  \"user\": \"example@gmail.com\",\r\n  \"password\": \"password\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n* Set application password:\r\n  * https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/185833\r\n* Enable IMAP:\r\n  * https://support.google.com/mail/answer/7126229?hl=en\r\n---\r\n\r\n> Project Kanban \\\r\n> https://github.com/orgs/Integration-Automation/projects/2/views/1\r\n> * Quickly Mail automation.\r\n> * SMTP support.\r\n> * IMAP4 support.\r\n> * Mail Thunder script.\r\n> * Automatically output all mail content as a file.\r\n> * Automatically send mail.\r\n> * Automatically send file.\r\n> * Socket server.\r\n> * Script Project & Template support.\r\n\r\n## install \r\n\r\n```\r\npip install je_mail_thunder\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Requires\r\n\r\n```\r\npython 3.8 or later\r\n```\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "je_mail_thunder.smtp", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "je_mail_thunder", "documentation": ["SMTP Wrapper"], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "je_mail_thunder.add_command_to_executor", "xref": {"fqname": "je_mail_thunder.utils.executor.action_executor.add_command_to_executor", "project": null}}, {"name": "je_mail_thunder.create_project_dir", "xref": {"fqname": "je_mail_thunder.utils.project.create_project_structure.create_project_dir", "project": null}}, {"name": "je_mail_thunder.execute_action", "xref": {"fqname": "je_mail_thunder.utils.executor.action_executor.execute_action", "project": null}}, {"name": "je_mail_thunder.execute_files", "xref": {"fqname": "je_mail_thunder.utils.executor.action_executor.execute_files", "project": null}}, {"name": "je_mail_thunder.get_dir_files_as_list", "xref": {"fqname": "je_mail_thunder.utils.file_process.get_dir_file_list.get_dir_files_as_list", "project": null}}, {"name": "je_mail_thunder.get_mail_thunder_os_environ", "xref": {"fqname": "je_mail_thunder.utils.save_mail_user_content.save_on_env.get_mail_th